webpackJsonp([0xc17519b1f87a],{447:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"Glen Cheney"}},markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Categorize, sort, and filter a responsive grid of items.</p>\n<h2>Hello world</h2>\n<p>Shuffle started as a side project while I was still at <a href="http://www.rit.edu">RIT</a> in December 2011. It used to be a jQuery plugin with a dependency on Modernizr. <a href="https://isotope.metafizzy.co/">Isotope</a>, a great layout plugin, inspired me to create my own with a focus on filtering and sorting items.</p>\n<h2>Iteration</h2>\n<p>Shuffle has evolved over the years. I rewrote it multiple times, removed its dependency on jQuery and Modernizr, added unit tests, added Rollup to generate bundles, and added TypeScript definitions.</p>\n<p>Along the way, it has also been used in multiple Odopod projects.</p>\n<p>Shuffle and its docs site has been a great outlet for me to try new web features and build tools, like Rollup and Gulp, before using them in client projects.</p>\n<!-- markdownlint-disable MD033 -->\n<video muted playsinline controls loop poster="/shuffle-poster.png">\n  <source src="/static/shuffle-d64f7d5c6ce177c0f5603abe32669d27.webm" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9,vorbis">\n  <source src="/static/shuffle-d51b9f6f0e2487ddf49a7784c9f3cc35.mp4" type="video/mp4">\n</video>\n<h2>Community</h2>\n<p>GitHub users have opened more than 150 issues with a wide variety of questions, feature requests, and bugs.</p>\n<h2>Current status</h2>\n<p>I actively maintain the package and occasionally contribute new features, documentation, and demos. npm users download the <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/shufflejs"><code class="language-text">shufflejs</code></a> package thousands of times per month.</p>',frontmatter:{title:"Shuffle",imageDescription:"Screenshot of the Shuffle package demo site.",href:"https://vestride.github.io/Shuffle/",tags:["open source","component","build systems"]}},hero:{sizes:{base64:"data:image/png;base64,",aspectRatio:1.7784131522516082,src:"/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-ef641.png",srcSet:"/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-c03bd.png 640w,\n/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-97ac5.png 1280w,\n/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-ef641.png 2488w",srcWebp:"/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-b43ba.webp",srcSetWebp:"/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-07a40.webp 640w,\n/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-55e7a.webp 1280w,\n/static/shuffle-0f575ec662941e67998f01bd9b94fa29-b43ba.webp 2488w",sizes:"(max-width: 2488px) 100vw, 2488px"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/shuffle/",heroImage:"/images/shuffle.png/",nextProject:{frontmatter:{title:"we.odopod"},fields:{slug:"/we-dot-odopod/"}}}}}});
